    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<thought\n>That \"letting go\" part is interesting. It sounds almost like you're saying that trying to hold on is just fighting an inevitable tide. If everything is just heading toward nothingness anyway, why does it feel like such a struggle to just... stop fighting it?",
